<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 11:53:55 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>草地上的美洲鸵</title><link>https://some.pics/6a0071d0b93fc</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一只大型、不会飞的鸟，很可能是美洲鸵，全身镜头拍摄，站在一片广阔的绿色草地上。这只鸟的羽毛呈灰褐色，脖子修长，正对着背景中央一棵高大、枝叶繁茂的绿树。树的右侧，一个小型的木栅栏围起了一小片草地，那里有另一只同种类的鸟正在休息。背景中，淡灰色的天空下，是平缓的绿色草坡。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A full shot of a large, flightless bird, likely a rhea, standing in a vast, green grassy field. The bird has grayish-brown feathers and a long neck, and it is facing toward a tall, leafy green tree in the center of the background. To the right of the tree, a small wooden picket fence encloses a patch of grass where another bird of the same species is resting. The background features a gentle grassy slope under a pale, overcast sky." height="2646" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/mangochutney/6a0071d0b93fc.jpg" width="1985"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://mangochutney.some.pics"&gt;@mangochutney&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 11:53:55 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>电池鼓包</title><link>https://some.pics/6a002890b2f36</link><description>&lt;p&gt;Framework 电池鼓包&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Framework battery swollen" height="3000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/sejo/6a002890b2f36.jpg" width="4000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://sejo.some.pics"&gt;@sejo&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 06:41:24 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>平板工作设置截图</title><link>https://some.pics/6a0025653f8bd</link><description>&lt;p&gt;我的平板工作设置截图&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Screenshot of my tablet work setup" height="1440" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/sejo/6a0025653f8bd.jpg" width="2304"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared 